---
title: Grilled Double Beef Burgers  with Bacon and Chipotle-Mustard Mayo
description: Time to fire up the grill for a delectable burger experience. These beauties are beefy, with two stacked patties, and they're topped with bacon, pickles, cheddar cheese and a tangy, zippy chipotle-mustard mayo, all on an artisan bun. Don't forget napkins – the best things in life are worth getting a little messy for!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R1020_W21_CA_RB162345-1_Main_2low-4c4e861a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/65f1d958d4f950689014ca9d.pdf
